name: Golden Eagle Regional Park in Sparks, Nevada, March 24 2013

desc.html: Facing eastward towards Multi-Use Field #1 at Golden Eagle Regional Park in Sparks, Nevada. Photo taken on March 24 2013. Football field at center, baseball fields slightly to the right. Foreground shows the natural desert grass in contrast to the turf, and in the background are the foothills of the Virginia Range/Eastern Sierras.
